{"item_id":"9a71ad5d53:0","text":"此 pattern 用于将几何线框作为 pattern assignment（图案分配）绘制出来。它可以与材质混合，也可以在 constant shader（常量 shader）中用作平面纹理。"}
{"item_id":"9a71ad5d53:1","text":"Input Parameters"}
{"item_id":"9a71ad5d53:2","text":"Wireframe Color"}
{"item_id":"9a71ad5d53:3","text":"绘制的线的颜色"}
{"item_id":"9a71ad5d53:4","text":"Background Color"}
{"item_id":"9a71ad5d53:5","text":"线框下方表面的颜色"}
{"item_id":"9a71ad5d53:6","text":"Wireframe Opacity"}
{"item_id":"9a71ad5d53:7","text":"绘制线条的不透明度或可见性"}
{"item_id":"9a71ad5d53:8","text":"Wireframe Width"}
{"item_id":"9a71ad5d53:9","text":"绘制的线的宽度或粗细"}
{"item_id":"9a71ad5d53:10","text":"Output Parameters"}
{"item_id":"9a71ad5d53:11","text":"resultRGB"}
{"item_id":"9a71ad5d53:12","text":"由该 pattern 生成的颜色分量（RGB）值。"}
